m_Anode1ExtendedEnergyRange.Name: Anode 1 Extended Energy Range
m_Anode1ExtendedEnergyRange.Description: When checked, a larger binding energy acquisition range is available. Some pass energies and energy step sizes may not be available. This option only applies to Al or Mg anode materials.
